{"type":null,"faqId":33954,"title":"个性化唤醒词该如何选择，唤醒效果才好？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1）唤醒词建议最少由4个音节组成（对应到中文由最少4个汉字组成）。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2）唤醒词要覆盖尽可能多的音节，避免出现相近或者重复的音节。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3）唤醒词相邻音节之间的差异尽可能大。例如“凯越在线”就是一个相邻音节差异大的一个例子；而“语音在线”前两个音节相近，不是一个好的唤醒词。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4）组成唤醒词的字如果具有以下属性，能够提高唤醒效果。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">5）开口度大、响度大、发音较清晰的字，韵母是复韵母。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">6）尽量选择一些平时较为不常说的词，以减少误唤醒的可能性。 </span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8656","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748775000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":30,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"语音唤醒,选择","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}